FT  26 APR 93 / Help lines for City today
Access to the City has been restricted by a police cordon shown above.
Unless told otherwise by their employers, staff employed in this area should
report to Guildhall where company representatives will be available to
handle queries. Further relocation information is available on 071-332-1500.
Advice to businesses is available on the City Corporation information line
071-332-3320 and 071-601-2800.
BR service into the City will be normal with Liverpool St station open at
5.30am. Tube services are unaffected except access to Bank station will be
via Monument station.
Businesses wanting calls rerouted should contact 0800-622245.
